on this collaboration

01:12:55.330 --> 01:12:58.370
between indigenous communities
and those of us who are allies

01:12:58.370 --> 01:13:02.380
in institutions - institutions
that should be doing this work

01:13:02.380 --> 01:13:05.230
because the materials in
our libraries, museums

01:13:05.230 --> 01:13:09.410
and archives got there in
very dubious circumstances.

01:13:09.410 --> 01:13:10.990
So we should be doing this work.

01:13:10.990 --> 01:13:12.630
&gt;&gt; Jane Anderson: And
