01:13:16.460 --> 01:13:18.620
at a community level, at
an institutional level

01:13:18.620 --> 01:13:21.970
and at a technical level
and those three parts,

01:13:21.970 --> 01:13:24.700
how we brought them together
and this project is partly

01:13:24.700 --> 01:13:26.870
because we were piloting
how they come together

01:13:26.870 --> 01:13:29.440
and we know much more about
kind of what that looks like.

01:13:29.440 --> 01:13:31.670
But at the same time
we're constantly thinking

01:13:31.670 --> 01:13:33.970
about what can this look
like for other communities

01:13:33.970 --> 01:13:35.310
and the sustainability of that.

01:13:35.310 --> 01:13:39.230
