01:13:57.710 --> 01:13:59.010
so that they already know
what their work flow would be,

01:13:59.010 --> 01:14:01.790
they know what is needed
at an institutional level.

01:14:01.790 --> 01:14:04.950
So that kind of helps smooth the
pathways and we've learned a lot

01:14:04.950 --> 01:14:06.810
of that from this
project itself.

01:14:06.810 --> 01:14:10.570
So that's kind of what the
next, the future looks like.

